Package objectcomparison

Class Book

  • java.lang.Object
    • objectcomparison.Book
  • class Book
extends java.lang.Object
    This Book class is a collection of book-related data values (i.e. Title, Author and Number of Pages), allowing me to demonstrate object comparison.

    The data values inside of this class are private, allowing access only through getter methods.

    Author:
    Dalton
